data.description: This stunning property offers the ideal blend of comfort, style, and location. With spacious living areas, modern amenities, and a beautiful backyard retreat with the pool! It's the ultimate family haven. Nestled in a charming neighborhood, this home provides easy access to schools, parks, and amenities. Don't miss your chance to make this address your own! It may look like a Tri-Level home, but it's NOT! This really is a 1 1/2 Story Home! There is a Primary Suite on the main with its own private bathroom! The upstairs has another primary suite so it can be a perfect fit for a teenager looking for their own space or for a blended family as well! Lovely updates have been made. New carpet has been done on the main as well as upstairs! Walk onto the deck from the dining area and have your tranquility in the backyard with the pool! Don't let this home slip by!  House has been Pre Inspected!
